Title: Five ways to reduce variance in A/B testing
Description: I use toy Monte Carlo simulations to demonstrate 5 ways to reduce variance in A/B testing: increase sample size, move towards a more even split, reduce variance in the metric definition, stratification and CUPED.

Title: Is Product Hunt dying?
Description: Ok, that might be an overdramatic title but Product Hunt is currently facing some serious issues. Mainly, their rule to feature products are quite opaque and arbitrary. It is harder to be featured on the home page:  This September on average 16 launches are featured per day In September 2023 the average was 47  The issue is ever clearer when looking at the share of featured launches (vs all launches):  Last year between 60% and 98% of launches were featured.
